# .dev.vars.example — template for local Cloudflare Worker vars
#
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (which is gitignored) and fill with LOCAL values only.
# NEVER put real production secrets here or commit a populated .dev.vars.
# In Step 1 the Worker shell uses NO bindings, so this is a placeholder.
#
# BINDINGS: TBD
# Example shape for later (do not uncomment with real values in source):
# DJZS_TRUST_TOKEN=replace-with-local-token
# ENVIRONMENT=development
